Package: gptr
Type: Package
Title: Structured Extraction Pipelines from Text with LLMs
Version: 0.4.8
Author: Francesco Monti
Maintainer: Francesco Monti <francesco.monti@outlook.it>
Description: Centers schema-based extraction workflows for data frames via
    'gpt_column()', with typed outputs, validation, retries, and audit-friendly
    debug metadata. Supports local or remote Large Language Model (LLM) APIs
    through OpenAI-compatible endpoints, with provider-aware helpers for model
    selection, single prompts, chat, and text-to-speech as supporting utilities.
